nowledged enough in their habits.<br><br>--Kelisk Mae'Lokh</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p><img src="http://publish.hometown.aol.com/bseh42/images/kelsig.jpg"></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukelisk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelisk</A> at: 2/15/02 3:00:37 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/upentapod.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pentapod</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/17/02 9:58:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=69.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Happy Valentine's Day</span><hr size=1> &lt;ooc&gt; Heh .... Didi doesn't have 5 tentacles, Pentapod does ... but thanks O-short-and-unspellable-one.<br><br>Edited out the &quot;human&quot; reference if it makes you happy Kelisk.  =)  &lt;/ooc&gt;<br><br>But soft?  A Teir'Dal?  It is to laugh .... thy hide may be harder than mine skin, but I'll wager thou'rt as soft inside as a wee snail slithering moistly about the hedges.  Come a little closer to my Spine Piercer and let us experiment, my friend... &lt;grins darkly and licks her lips&gt; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukelisk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelisk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>No, YOU'RE evil</span><br>  Posts: 133<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/18/02 7:34:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=69.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td